Now, if there are in your shelves the vinyl disks embedded, with rock art, jazz or blues, you probably dream of at least one such gramophone.
The same is true of music during movements, i.e. compressed music, to say it in a simplified way - MP3 music.
There are also categories depending on price and quality.
For one, it may be unacceptable to spend eight thousand crowns for a reader, in the same way that a Pink Floyd fan would have trouble bearing earphones purchased for twenty crowns in the market.
There are two extremes between which there is enough room for everyone.
The choice is wide.
The lifespan of batteries is also decisive
Some high-end music players are capable of much more than just music reading, but these are unknown functions, of course, of most mobiles.
