The AAC (format used by Apple firm and its iPods) is less common than it is.
High-end furniture also allows, for example, the purchase of online music.
Just visit the corresponding operator's web pages (or those of another provider) from the mobile phone and buy the song or album in question.
This service alone should be a compelling reason for obtaining a musical motive.
