And if the free theme can be a means of spreading it in the homes, it's just in business, that Open Office will then try the big challenge, which can already count on various projects carried out in public administration and schools.
Apart from the realities that provide a training, consultation and assistance service, ideal for small and medium-sized enterprises, which could also open up to business prospects.
